ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好耐冇見</blockquote><br />\n你係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有上過q拿？</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你仲認得我 你都幾犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成34年前既事</blockquote><br />\n哈哈 記得你舊登都有作<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"052e9758eb101f71ef159586011220c92aafd0e9","tid":394944,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好耐冇見</blockquote><br />\n你係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有上過q拿？</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你仲認得我 你都幾犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成34年前既事</blockquote><br />\n哈哈 記得你舊登都有作<br />\n加油</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}